    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Family Size vs. Purchasing Behavior'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='651' maxwidth='1350' minheight='651' minwidth='1350' preset-index='17' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='42243' id='4' type-v2='text' w='62222' x='296' y='8909'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='14'>Findings:</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='12'>Æ </run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='12'>Data indicates that despite lower order velocity, single-person households exhibit the highest average order value (AOV). On the other hand, three-person families order most often and spend the highest total amount</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='14'>Recommendations:</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='12'> To boost engagement, Zomato can increase interaction by tailoring promotions toward larger families and encouraging ratings from all user types. Promoting popular food categories through targeted marketing will further enhance engagement</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='6912' id='5' type-v2='text' w='34593' x='32741' y='614'>
